96
00:10:42.465 --> 00:10:43.847
<i>- From him?
- From everything.</i>

97
00:10:43.882 --> 00:10:47.347
<i>- That's not possible. Carrie.
- It used to be.</i>

98
00:10:47.382 --> 00:10:49.638
Ana.

99
00:10:49.673 --> 00:10:52.680
