Trust me. it can't
get any fucking harder.

122
00:12:35.347 --> 00:12:37.930
Hey. get those last
three pallets loaded.

123
00:12:37.965 --> 00:12:39.597
That truck should have
been on the road hours ago.

124
00:12:45.930 --> 00:12:47.972
Motherfucker.

125
00:12:54.472 --> 00:12:57.138
<i>Mr. Proctor. I was not
expecting you today.</i>

126
00:12:57.173 --> 00:12:59.388
