the burden of beauty.

211
00:18:50.882 --> 00:18:51.847
[whimpering]

212
00:18:51.882 --> 00:18:54.597
[shrieks]

213
00:18:57.513 --> 00:19:01.305
[dog growling. barking]

214
00:19:01.340 --> 00:19:04.472
Hesher here chased down
a rabid possum a while back.

215
00:19:07.013 --> 00:19:10.097
He ain't been the same since.

216
00:19:10.132 --> 00:19:12.722
[screaming]

217
00:19:21.013 --> 00:19:24.097
[screaming]

218
00:19:30.055 --> 00:19:32.222
[groans]

219
00:19:32.257 --> 00:19:35.097
[screaming]

220
00:19:48.138 --> 00:19:50.513
Jesus...

221
00:19:50.548 --> 00:19:51.388
[dog barking]

222
00:19:54.972 --> 00:19:57.097
<i>[Rebecca laughing]</i>

223
00:19:59.180 --> 00:20:01.222
<i>[laughing continues]</i>

224
00:20:03.180 --> 00:20:05.972
[panting]

225
00:20:06.007 --> 00:20:08.388
You fucking bitch.

226
00:20:10.972 --> 00:20:11.930
[screams]

227
00:20:11.965 --> 00:20:16.847
[screaming]

228
00:20:16.882 --> 00:20:22.388
Oh... Jesus Christ!

229
00:20:22.423 --> 00:20:25.763
You okay?
Look at me. Look at me.

230
00:20:25.798 --> 00:20:26.847
Come on.

231
00:20:26.882 --> 00:20:28.513
Come on.

232
00:20:30.930 --> 00:20:33.263
<i>Rebecca! Rebecca!</i>

233
00:20:39.222 --> 00:20:41.430
Hey. Rebecca.

234
00:20:41.465 --> 00:20:43.347
<i>We don't have time for this.</i>

235
00:20:47.305 --> 00:20:48.775
Rebecca.

236
00:20:56.763 --> 00:21:00.559
